EN: Readers can expand their knowledge by reading different books.

ZH: 作家需要考虑读者的喜好来写作。
EN: Writers need to consider the preferences of the readers when writing.

ZH: 读者对于小说的结局感到非常满意。
EN: Readers are very satisfied with the ending of the novel.

