EN: Authors often interact with readers to understand their opinions.

ZH: 读者们都期待着这本小说的发行。
EN: Readers are looking forward to the release of this novel.

ZH: 读者们对该问题的态度各不相同。
EN: Readers have different attitudes towards the issue.

